}}'''斑疹傷寒'''（{{lang-en|Typhus}}），是由[[立克次體|立克次體]]引起的[[傳染病|傳染病]]<ref>{{DorlandsDict|eight/000112663|Typhus}}</ref>，可分為：[[流行性斑疹伤寒|流行性斑疹伤寒]]、[[叢林斑疹傷寒|丛林斑疹伤寒]]（[[恙蟲病|恙蟲病]]）與[[地方性斑疹傷寒|地方性斑疹傷寒]]（[[鼠型斑疹伤寒|鼠型斑疹伤寒]]）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Typhus fevers home|url=https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/index.html|accessdate=2021-02-26|date=2020-11-13|last=|work=|publisher=[[美国疾控中心|美国疾控中心]]|language=en-us|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326231028/https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Epidemic and Endemic Typhus|title=Radiology of Infectious Diseases: Volume 2|url=https://doi.org/10.1007/978-94-017-9876-1_8|publisher=Springer Netherlands|date=2015|location=Dordrecht|isbn=978-94-017-9876-1|pages=89–94|doi=10.1007/978-94-017-9876-1_8#:~:text=the%20whole%20course%20of%20epidemic,occurrence%20in%20autumns%20and%20winters.|language=en|first=Li|last=Li|first2=Guiying|last2=Li|editor-first=Hongjun|editor-last=Li|access-date=2021-02-26|archive-date=2021-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211018031905/https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-94-017-9876-1_8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<!-- <ref name=CDC2017In/> -->症狀包括發燒、頭痛和皮疹。<ref name=CDC2017In>{{cite web|title=Typhus Fevers|url=https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/index.html|website=www.cdc.gov|accessdate=26 March 2017|language=en-us|date=7 March 2017|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326231028/https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>症狀通常在接觸病原體後一至兩週出現<ref name=CDC2017He/>

[[傷寒|傷寒]]由細菌感染引起。<!-- <ref name=CDC2017In/> -->流行性斑疹傷寒是[[体虱|体虱]]傳播的立克次體引起的，叢林型斑疹傷寒是恙滿幼蟲傳播的恙蟲病立克次體引起的，鼠性斑疹傷寒是鼠蚤傳播的地方性斑疹傷寒立克次體引起的。<ref name=CDC2017In/>

斑疹傷寒沒有疫苗。<!-- <ref name=CDC2017Epi/><ref name=CDC2017Scu/><ref name=CDC2017Mu/> -->預防方法是避免接觸傳播疾病的生物。<ref name=CDC2017Epi>{{cite web|title=Epidemic Typhus|url=https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/epidemic/index.html|website=www.cdc.gov|accessdate=26 March 2017|language=en-us|date=7 March 2017|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326230950/https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/epidemic/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CDC2017Mu>{{cite web|title=Murine Typhus|url=https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/murine/index.html|website=www.cdc.gov|accessdate=26 March 2017|language=en-us|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326230521/https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/murine/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CDC2017Scu>{{cite web|title=Scrub Typhus|url=https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/scrub/index.html|website=www.cdc.gov|accessdate=26 March 2017|language=en-us|date=7 March 2017|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326230903/https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/scrub/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>治療方法是使用[[四環素|四環素]]抗生素。<ref name=CDC2017He>{{cite web|title=Information for Health Care Providers|url=https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/healthcare-providers/index.html|website=www.cdc.gov|accessdate=26 March 2017|language=en-us|date=7 March 2017|archive-date=2017-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327075824/https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/healthcare-providers/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>流行性斑疹傷寒常於衛生環境差和擁擠的地方爆發<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO {{!}} Typhus|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs162/en/|website=www.who.int|accessdate=26 March 2017|date=May 1997|archive-date=2017-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327080029/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs162/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但現在已經少見了。<ref name=CDC2017Epi/>叢林型斑疹傷寒可見於東南亞、日本和澳洲北部。<ref name=CDC2017Scu/>鼠性斑疹傷寒見於熱帶和亞熱帶地區。<ref name=CDC2017Mu/> 

斑疹傷寒的記載至少可以追溯到1528年，<!-- <ref name=Ben2014/> -->源於希臘語typhus (τύφος) ，意指迷茫，用於形容患者受感染後的精神狀態。<ref name=Ben2014>{{cite book|last1=Bennett|first1=John E.|last2=Dolin|first2=Raphael|last3=Blaser|first3=Martin J.|title=Mandell, Douglas, and Bennett's Principles and Practice of Infectious Diseases E-Book|date=2014|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=9780323263733|page=2217|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=73pYBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA2217|language=en|access-date=2017-06-20|archive-date=2020-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224051246/https://books.google.ca/books?id=73pYBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA2217|dead-url=no}}</ref> 斑疹傷寒與傷寒是不同細菌引起的不同病症。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Evans|first1=Alfred S.|last2=Brachman|first2=Philip S.|title=Bacterial Infections of Humans: Epidemiology and Control|date=2013|publisher=Springer|isbn=9781461553274|page=839|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=dPDdBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA839|language=en|access-date=2017-06-20|archive-date=2020-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224051200/https://books.google.ca/books?id=dPDdBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA839|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==病理學==
===流行性斑疹傷寒===
[[流行性斑疹伤寒|流行性斑疹伤寒]]，又稱人蝨型斑疹傷寒，是由{{link-en|普氏立克次體|Rickettsia prowazekii}}（''Rickettsia Prowazeki''）引起的急性传染病，屬於“人—蝨—人”傳播的疾病，人是唯一的宿主，[[体虱|体虱]]是傳播媒介，常流行於冬季或寒帶地區。普氏立克次体在体虱胃肠道上皮细胞中生长繁殖，经體蝨粪便排出体外，人是經由揉擠蝨糞或壓擠蝨子入叮咬處或表皮傷口而感染，有頭痛、畏寒、虛脫、發燒和全身疼痛的現象，第五至六天會出現斑點，有顯著毒血症，約發燒二週後症狀迅速消失而恢復，死亡率約10%～40%。此病可能復發，但復發症狀較溫和。近年來，流行性斑疹傷寒的傳染已大為減少，主要見於[[非洲|非洲]]。

[[布里尔-津瑟病|布里尔-津瑟病]]，又称复发性斑疹伤寒，是延迟发病的流行性斑疹伤寒<ref name=":02">{{Cite web|title=Epidemic typhus|url=https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/epidemic/index.html|accessdate=2021-02-28|date=2020-11-13|last=|work=|publisher=[[美国疾控中心|美国疾控中心]]|language=en-us|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326230950/https://www.cdc.gov/typhus/epidemic/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===地方性斑疹伤寒===
[[地方性斑疹伤寒|地方性斑疹伤寒]]，又稱鼠型（或蚤型）斑疹傷寒，是一种自然疫源性疾病，是由莫氏立克次體（''Rickettsia Mooseri''），又稱斑疹傷寒立克次氏體（''Rickettsia typhi''）透過鼠蚤傳播的急性傳染病，[[印鼠客蚤|印鼠客蚤]]是传播媒介，人是受害者。屬於“鼠—蚤—人”传播循环，其臨床特徵與流行性斑疹傷寒相似，有頭痛、惡寒的情況，但病情輕、病程短，潛伏期為6～14日，死亡率極低。氯黴素及四環素為其特效藥物，病癒後的復發性低。地方型斑疹傷寒發病地區散佈於全球，多見於[[熱帶|熱帶]]和[[亞熱帶|亞熱帶]]地區。

==流行==
根據[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]資料，斑疹傷寒每年造成每百萬人中0.2人死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.who.int/whosis/en/ |title=WHO Statistical Information System (WHOSIS) |access-date=2014-08-09 |archive-date=2010-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100221035844/http://www.who.int/whosis/en/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 20世纪大流行 ===
[[第一次世界大战|第一次世界大战]]以及[[俄国内战|俄国内战]]期间，[[流行性斑疹伤寒|流行性斑疹伤寒]]造成[[苏俄|苏俄]]境内200-300万人死亡（1918年-1922年），约2000-3000万人感染，是历史上[[流行病列表|致死人数最多的流行病之一]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=TYPHUS AND ITS CONTROL IN RUSSIA, 1870-1940|author=K. DAVID PATTERSON|url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/0AF993E555D30A9F8DCD864F4DDD4344/S0025727300058725a.pdf/div-class-title-typhus-and-its-control-in-russia-1870-1940-div.pdf|journal=Medical History|issue=37|doi=|others=|year=1993|volume=|page=|pmid=|access-date=2020-12-22|archive-date=2020-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224051210/https://www.cambridge.org/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/0AF993E555D30A9F8DCD864F4DDD4344/S0025727300058725a.pdf/div-class-title-typhus-and-its-control-in-russia-1870-1940-div.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 与此同时，在[[波兰|波兰]]和[[罗马尼亚|罗马尼亚]]也出现了疫情。此次大流行是近代史上斑疹伤寒最大规模的一次[[疾病爆发|爆发]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Typhus in World War I|url=https://microbiologysociety.org/publication/past-issues/world-war-i/article/typhus-in-world-war-i.html|accessdate=2020-12-22|author=|date=|last=|first=|format=|work=|publisher=Microbiology Society|language=|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308213901/https://microbiologysociety.org/publication/past-issues/world-war-i/article/typhus-in-world-war-i.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[西方战线_(第一次世界大战)|西方战线]]为士兵特意建立了“除[[虱|虱]]站（Delousing station）”以应对疫情，但[[东方战线_(第一次世界大战)|东方战线]]的疫情导致军队损失惨重，仅[[塞尔维亚|塞尔维亚]]就有15万人受感染死亡。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Typhus on The Eastern Front|url=https://www.kumc.edu/wwi/index-of-essays/typhus-on-the-eastern-front.html|accessdate=2020-12-22|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[堪萨斯大学|堪萨斯大学]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224051223/https://www.kumc.edu/wwi/index-of-essays/typhus-on-the-eastern-front.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 总体[[病死率|病死率]]在10%-40%之间，且该[[流行病|流行病]]也成为当时相关医护人员死亡的主因。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Typhus - Louseborne|url=https://open.alberta.ca/dataset/02ec895a-f9f7-43e9-b3d2-4811679701c2/resource/e3651662-8bc7-4edd-81cd-3b4cf03661e6/download/guidelines-typhus-louseborne-2018-05.pdf|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Alberta Health Public Health Disease Management Guidelines|language=|archive-date=2019-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219141039/https://open.alberta.ca/dataset/02ec895a-f9f7-43e9-b3d2-4811679701c2/resource/e3651662-8bc7-4edd-81cd-3b4cf03661e6/download/guidelines-typhus-louseborne-2018-05.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[戰俘營|战俘营]]中也有大量死亡。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Outbreak of epidemic typhus in Russia|url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(05)79799-3/abstract|last=Tarasevich|first=Irina|last2=Rydkina|first2=Elena|date=1998-10-03|journal=The Lancet|issue=9134|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(05)79799-3|volume=352|pages=1151|language=en|issn=0140-6736|pmid=9798622|last3=Raoult|first3=Didier}}</ref>

